      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-80f1-9a9b-f94d6070b331",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors wish to go develop a recommender system approach that predicts student performance. Authors compare the performance of their approach to traditional methods such as logistic/linear regression methods.",
